&lt;li&gt;Explain variances against budget and forecast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support planning and decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present financial insights clearly to senior stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems &amp;amp; Process Transformation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Play a key role in the implementation of a new global billing system, ensuring:
&lt;ul&gt;
